snippet.title: The Dark Crystal: Age of Resistance Tactics | Pre-Order Trailer
snippet.description:
Fantasy turn-based tactics RPG, The Dark Crystal: Age of Resistance Tactics is now available for pre-order on Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Steam and GoG:
http://DarkCrystalTactics.com

Launching on February 4th for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation®4, Xbox One, and PC, The Dark Crystal: Age of Resistance Tactics is a strategy game where you will lead a fledgling resistance of Gelfling against their oppressive overlords, the Skeksis, across more than 50 unique turn-based tactics battles. Pre-order today!

Pre-order now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1097790/The_Dark_Crystal_Age_of_Resistance_Tactics/

Pre-order now on Nintendo Switch!
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/the-dark-crystal-age-of-resistance-tactics-switch/

Pre-order now on GoG!
https://www.gog.com/game/the_dark_crystal_age_of_resistance_tactics

Pre-Order now on Xbox!
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/the-dark-crystal-age-of-resistance-tactics/9nzwxt6vmgg8?activetab=pivot:overviewtab

Pre-order now on the EME launcher!
https://store.enmasse.com/darkcrystaltactics/
